Project Title: Development of Confidential Web Portal for Road Safety Reporting with Geospatial Mapping

All rights reserved.

This software project and its documentation were developed as an academic project. The work focuses on the use of web and geospatial technologies for confidential road safety reporting and administrative road safety management.

Primary technologies used in this project include:
- PHP
- Laravel
- MySQL
- Bootstrap
- JavaScript
- HTML
- CSS
- Google Maps API

